    "announcerProfile": "arena-announcer",
    "gameStart": "The holographic arena grid flickers to life in the undercity pit. Neon signs cast harsh shadows as two street fighters jack in. The crowd's neural feeds buzz with anticipation. Begin!",
    "roundStart": [
      "Targeting reticles flash as a new round of chrome-on-chrome combat initiates!",
      "The arena's holographic counter ticks over — another round begins beneath the flickering neon!",
      "Servos whine and cyberlimbs lock into fighting stance. The combatants reload for another exchange!",
      "The EMP dampeners reset with a crackle. A new round begins in the neon haze!",
      "Adrenaline injectors hiss. The fighters emerge from the holographic smoke for another round."
    ],
    "roundEndTie": [
      "Systems deadlocked — neither combatant gains the advantage. A digital stalemate!",
      "Evenly matched chrome! Their augments cancel each other out. No ground gained!"
    ],
    "criticalHit": [
      "A devastating strike! Sparks fly from shattered cybernetics!",
      "Direct hit to the neural jack! The crowd roars through their implants!",
      "Chrome buckles under the force of that blow! Absolutely brutal!"
    ],
    "criticalMiss": [
      "A system glitch! The targeting HUD flickers and the strike goes wide!",
      "Cybernetic malfunction at the worst possible moment!",
      "Neural lag spikes and the augmented limb freezes mid-swing!"
    ],
    "lowHpTension": [
      "Warning alerts flash across both fighters' HUDs as sparks trail from damaged implants.",
      "The air reeks of burnt circuitry and desperation. This bout nears its end.",
      "Systems critical on both sides. One more precision strike could flatline them both."
    ]
